    <h5>40 games</h5>
    <ul>
        <li>12 games vs. division &mdash; 3 teams &times; 4</li>
        <li>16 games vs. rest of conference &mdash; 8 teams &times; 2</li>
        <li>12 games vs. other conference &mdash; 12 teams &times; 1</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>2023</h4>
    <h5>36 games</h5>
    <ul>
        <li>12 games vs. division &mdash; 3 teams &times; 2, 2 teams &times; 3</li>
