        <li>12 games vs. other conference &mdash; 12 teams &times; 1</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>2022</h4>
    <h5>28 games</h5>
    <ul>
        <li>10 games vs. division &mdash; 5 teams &times; 2</li>
        <li>6 games vs. rest of conference &mdash; 6 teams &times; 1</li>
        <li>12 games vs. other conference &mdash; 12 teams &times; 1</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>2021</h4>
    <h5>16 games</h5>
    <ul>
        <li>10 games vs. division &mdash; 5 teams &times; 2</li>
        <li>6 games vs. other division &mdash; 6 teams &times; 1</li>
    </ul>
</div>